{"tid":223071,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[乒乓球]集中討論區","createTime":"2017-04-30T05:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T12:15:39.000Z","uid":90101,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f3d3ba48cd2a804908b68b264fe9a9d1de298aed","tid":223071,"uid":90101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"見好似未有關於乒乓球嘅集中討論區 希望多個地方比大家 約戰 討論下技術 器材等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3thbwnc8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3thbwnc8&h=3f85d32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />《混雙》 今年上映<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/npoj6tes\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnpoj6tes&h=b1a4e0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐孝元(韓國削球手)<br />\n<br />\n港隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kqn3j17s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkqn3j17s&h=8b105fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大聖-黃鎮廷(現役直拍橫打最強)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐洲隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2nxihycu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2nxihycu&h=d9161d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n長青樹-瓦爾德內爾(瑞典，史上第一位男子大滿貫，征戰40多年)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5teykold\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5teykold&h=6f07d192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波爾(德國名將)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2a8t3qhd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2a8t3qhd&h=43c55fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奥恰洛夫(德國新一代)<br />\n<br />\n中國隊<br />\n第一代:雙子星時代<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qeuyhw8a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqeuyhw8a&h=491a100a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉國樑(中國第一位男子大滿貫，現中國隊總教練)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w9b68tg1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%